<item>
            <title>[LU-12770] Sanity quota test fixes for zfs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12770</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current detection for project quota on zfs uses:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160; zpool update -v | grep&#160;project_quota&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It seems this should be:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160; zpool get all | grep&#160;project_quota&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also using tune2fs / and debugfs on zfs does not have the desired effect.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
